# Code
```
class Solution {
    public int searchInsert(int[] nums, int target) {
        int start = 0;
        int end = nums.length-1;

        while (start <= end) {

        int mid = start + (end - start) / 2;

        if (target < nums[mid]) {
            end = mid - 1;
        }

        else if (target > nums[mid]) {
            start = mid + 1;
        }

        else {
            return mid;
        }
    }
    return start;
    }
}
```

