We can Solved this question using Two approach.

1. Using Linear Search (Brute Force).
2. Using Binary Search (Optimize).

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
We can easily understand the All the approaches by seeing the code which is easy to understand with comments.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
